chart.name: Read Throughput
chart.programText:
A = data('ReadThroughput', filter=filter('namespace', 'AWS/RDS') and filter('stat', 'mean') and filter('DBInstanceIdentifier', '*')).mean(by=['DBInstanceIdentifier']).publish(label='A', enable=False)
B = (A).min().publish(label='B')
C = (A).percentile(pct=10).publish(label='C')
D = (A).percentile(pct=50).publish(label='D')
E = (A).percentile(pct=90).publish(label='E')
F = (A).max().publish(label='F')

chart.name: R/W IOPS 24h Change %
chart.programText:
A = data('ReadIOPS', filter=filter('namespace', 'AWS/RDS') and filter('DBInstanceIdentifier', 'myrds') and filter('stat', 'mean')).mean(over='1h').publish(label='A', enable=False)
B = data('WriteIOPS', filter=filter('namespace', 'AWS/RDS') and filter('DBInstanceIdentifier', 'myrds') and filter('stat', 'mean')).mean(over='1h').publish(label='B', enable=False)
C = (A).timeshift('1d').publish(label='C', enable=False)
D = (B).timeshift('1d').publish(label='D', enable=False)
E = ((A-C)/C*100).publish(label='E')
F = ((B-D)/D*100).publish(label='F')
